sequenceDiagram
    participant U as 用户
    participant FE as 前端 AppShell
    participant API as SseController
    participant MGR as SseEmitterManager
    participant Redis as Redis

    U->>FE: 登录成功
    FE->>FE: stores/message.connectSSE()
    FE->>API: GET /api/message/subscribe?token=xxx
    API->>API: jwtUtil.getUserId(token)
    API->>MGR: addEmitter(userId, emitter)
    MGR->>MGR: emitters.put(userId, emitter)
    API-->>FE: SSE 长连接建立
    FE->>API: GET /api/message/unread-count
    API->>Redis: getUnreadCount(userId)
    Redis-->>FE: 未读数 = 3
    FE->>FE: 导航栏显示红点(3)
